# SaaS / White-Label

## Branding

- Read site name and logos from `BrandingSettingsService`, not hardcoded strings
- Theme colors from `ThemeSettingsService` тЖТ CSS variables on `<html>`
- Footer copy from `FooterSettingsService`

## Admin chrome

- Use generic labels: "Admin", "Courses", "Content", "Settings"
- Sport-specific copy belongs in CMS seed content or course data, not admin shell

## Avoid in shared components

- Hardcoded "365daysdarts", "darts", sport-specific nav labels in reusable layout (migrate to CMS nav or settings when possible)

## New features

When adding public-facing chrome, ask: "Would this work for a tennis or soccer tenant?" If no, make it configurable.
